{
  "text": "The D708A transgene was bred onto a Rag1 \u00c0/\u00c0 background to generate D708A-R1 \u00c0/\u00c0 mice, which exhibit blocks at the pro-B and pro-T stages of lymphocyte development equivalent to those of R1 \u00c0/\u00c0 mice (Figures S1A and S1C available online). To allow analysis of pre-B and pre-T cells, D708A-R1 \u00c0/\u00c0 mice were bred with mice harboring a functionally rearranged B1-8i Igh allele [CITATION_1] or the 2B4 Tcrb transgene [CITATION_2] to generate D708A-R1 \u00c0/\u00c0 H or D708A-R1",
